                    <div class="exc-description">
                        <p>Renegade rows are a dynamic exercise that combine the intensity of a plank with the power of a row. In a single exercise, you can blast your core while also strengthening your back, biceps, and triceps.</p><p>If you’re not sure how to perform this exercise or work it into your gym split, don’t worry. Today, we’ll cover everything you need to know about this unbeatable exercise. Let’s get into it.</p>                    </div>
